Hi!
 
I am sorry, I have had no reply. I wanted to make sure you had received my email with the details of Artistar Jewels and wanted to ask you if you had any questions about it.

I think it is a great opportunity to show your creations internationally and be in contact with several important galleries.

I would like to remind you to fill in the application form in case you are interested in the 10th edition of Artistar Jewels:

ok perfect, thank you! I sent the info there :) Look forward your kind feedback!

Hello Carina! this is Gloria from the Milano Jewelry Week, I am contacting you because we are selecting the designer for the next exhibition.
I send you a general mail but I would like to give you more info. Can I send them via mail? or we can schedule a call :)
